  "subject": "Add MaxRAMPercentage=50% JVM default to Dockerfile",
  "commit_message": "Add MaxRAMPercentage=50% JVM default to Dockerfile\n\nWithout explicit MaxRAMPercentage, the JVM defaults to 25% of\ncontainer memory for heap while non-heap grows unconstrained.\nSetting 50% provides a balanced default that works with the\nreduced container limits from OOM-3391.\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4352\nChange-Id: I83e72e0a7781f1bf51d5a41127808855c194f857\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
